    <char style="w" strong="H5674">Le</char> destructeur vient <char style="w" strong="H5921">contre</char> toi, Ninive! Garde <char style="w" strong="H8085">la</char> forteresse, surveille <char style="w" strong="H5674">le</char> chemin, fortifie <char style="w" strong="H7999">tes</char> reins, <char style="w" strong="H3063">et</char> rassemble toutes <char style="w" strong="H7999">tes</char> forces. <verse eid="NAM 2:1" /><verse number="2" style="v" sid="NAM 2:2" /><char style="w" strong="H6440">Car</char> l'Éternel rétablit <char style="w" strong="H6440">la</char> gloire <char style="w" strong="H6440">de</char> Jacob <char style="w" strong="H1870">comme</char> <char style="w" strong="H6440">la</char> gloire d'Israël, parce <char style="w" strong="H6440">que</char> <char style="w" strong="H6440">les</char> pillards <char style="w" strong="H6440">les</char> <char style="w" strong="H6440">ont</char> pillés <char style="w" strong="H5927">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H3966">qu'ils</char> <char style="w" strong="H6440">ont</char> ravagé <char style="w" strong="H6440">leurs</char> vignes. <verse eid="NAM 2:2" /><verse number="3" style="v" sid="NAM 2:3" /><char style="w" strong="H7725">Le</char> bouclier <char style="w" strong="H7725">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H7843">ses</char> hommes vaillants <char style="w" strong="H3068">est</char> rouge; <char style="w" strong="H7725">les</char> guerriers <char style="w" strong="H3068">sont</char> vêtus d'écarlate; l'acier <char style="w" strong="H3068">des</char> chars étincelle, <char style="w" strong="H7725">au</char> jour <char style="w" strong="H3478">où</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">il</char> <char style="w" strong="H3068">se</char> prépare, <char style="w" strong="H3478">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H7725">les</char> lances <char style="w" strong="H3068">sont</char> agitées. <verse eid="NAM 2:3" /><verse number="4" style="v" sid="NAM 2:4" /><char style="w" strong="H3117">Les</char> <char style="w" st